<li>Bikhchandani, Sushil, Hirshleifer, David, and Welch, Ivo. "A Theory of Fads, Fashion, Custom, and Cultural Change as <a href="/wiki/Informational_cascade" title="Informational cascade" class="mw-redirect">Informational Cascades</a>." <i>Journal of Political Economy</i>, Vol. 100, No.5, pp. 992-1026, 1992.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Wilfred_Trotter" title="Wilfred Trotter">Wilfred Trotter</a>, <i>The Instincts of the Herd in Peace and War</i>, 1914.</li>
