<li>Rook, Laurens. "An Economic Psychological Approach to Herd Behavior." Journal of Economic Issues 40.1 (2006): 75-95.</li>
<li>Hamilton, W D. Geometry for the Selfish Herd. Diss. Imperial College, 1970.</li>
